Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.45,0:04:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即將發起一場核戰爭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}was on the brink of launching a nuclear war.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.16,0:04:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在與超級大國進行的裁軍談判中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}With the superpowers now launching disarmament talks,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.84,0:04:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}蘇聯-東歐分部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.04,0:04:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俄羅斯人民渴望他們能夠成功\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the Russian people are eager for them to succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.29,0:04:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格萊姆斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Grimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.38,0:04:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五分鐘后去沃利的辦公室開會\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Staffer, Wally's office, five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.42,0:04:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臨時抱佛腳\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Last-second heebie-jeebies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.65,0:04:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰慌了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Who panicked?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.66,0:04:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞姆斯  他快崩潰了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ames. He's got his head up his ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.93,0:04:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可真是慈悲心腸的典范\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You are a model of compassion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.96,0:04:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一看到他們就打招呼來著\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I call them as I see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.33,0:04:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你有這么多朋友的原因\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Which is why you have so many friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.36,0:04:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你還是愛我的  對吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, but you still love me, though, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.43,0:04:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫斯科時間下午六點半\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey. 6:00 P.M. in Moscow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.16,0:04:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道你的情報專員在哪兒嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you know where your Case Officer is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.45,0:04:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和克格勃一起喝得酩酊大醉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Getting drunk with the KGB.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.84,0:04:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五分鐘后有個會\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, staffer in five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.39,0:04:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在奧斯丁的辦公室  我記得\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Austin's office, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.72,0:04:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  路易莎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thanks, Louisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.71,0:05:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  羅琳\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Good morning, Lorraine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.81,0:05:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚傳來的情報\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nightly cable traffic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.71,0:05:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看  兩個常規報告  一個夜間行動\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Okay, two routine, one night action,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.10,0:05:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三個緊急文件  都是保密案件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}three immediate, all restricted cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.10,0:05:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-對了  要開個...  -會\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Also, there's a... - Staffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.88,0:05:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}珊蒂·格萊姆斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}4005
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.04,0:05:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是個錯誤\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.38,0:05:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不想帶著現金過邊境\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He doesn't want to take the cash across the border.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.69,0:05:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在蘇聯境內秘密交接金錢的風險太大了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dead-dropping money inside the Soviet Union's too risky.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.95,0:05:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,間諜拿到錢之后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The asset picks up the package
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.91,0:05:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,容易被人看到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and anyone could see him with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.24,0:05:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但讓他把錢帶在身上也沒好到哪去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But having him travel with the money is just as bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.98,0:05:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邊界線到處都是克格勃探員\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There are KGB agents at every border crossing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.45,0:05:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊蒂  情報放置點可藏不住兩萬盧布\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sandy, 20,000 rubles is not easy to conceal in a dead-drop location.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.53,0:05:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是他們發現他身上有錢  會殺了他的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If they find cash on him, they'll kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.24,0:05:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身帶巨款的人不一定是間諜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Cash could be a sign of criminal activity,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.98,0:05:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可能是犯罪分子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}not espionage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.42,0:05:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  這是向他表明即使在蘇聯境內\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And anyway, this is a perfect opportunity to show him
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.63,0:05:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也能與他取得聯系的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that we are capable of communicating with him
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.00,0:05:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕佳機會\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}inside the Soviet Union.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.82,0:05:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這名間諜代號為巨錨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The asset code named GT Weigh
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.03,0:05:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一名克格勃高層探員\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}is a highly placed KGB officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.93,0:05:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他曾是我們在七十年代最早的一批間諜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He was a primary asset for us in the '70s.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.58,0:05:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他給我們提供了許多海外行動的珍貴情報\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He gave us invaluable intel on overseas operations.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.41,0:05:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十周前他重新露面時\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When he resurfaced 10 weeks ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.36,0:06:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們答應他會多付錢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}we promised him more money,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.89,0:06:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得好好履行這個承諾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and we need to make good on that promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.34,0:06:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只這樣  我們得向他  向我們自己\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But more than that, we need to prove to him --
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.66,0:06:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,證明我們有能力在克格勃的眼皮底下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To ourselves -- that we can run a viable operation inside KGB territory
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.57,0:06:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展開行動\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}right under their noses.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.05,0:06:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什么要用如此寶貴的間諜來證明\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Okay. Why prove it with such a valuable asset?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.47,0:06:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這只是嘗試  我們換個小人物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If this is a test case, let's use a small fry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.27,0:06:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是嘗試  里克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This isn't a test case, Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.67,0:06:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一向這么做  這是我們的行事手段\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's how we do business. It's what we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.83,0:06:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Art.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.30,0:06:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別問我  沃利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't look at me, Wally.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.23,0:06:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿高工資的人是你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's why they pay you the big bucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.37,0:06:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把錢放到放置點\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Drop the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.91,0:06:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴莫斯科分站往下行動\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tell Moscow to move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.66,0:06:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有信息及時匯報\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And keep me updated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.26,0:06:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保密通信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Restricted access.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.45,0:06:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫斯科方面立即行動\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Immediate action traffic, Moscow station.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.44,0:06:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按已探討方案放置巨錨資金\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Proceed with GT Weigh funds dead drop as discussed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.07,0:07:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,及時匯報\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Update ASAP.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.33,0:07:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}美國領事館\N莫斯科
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.55,0:07:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"繼續巨錨行動"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"Proceed with GT Weigh."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"放置資金"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"Funds drop."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.42,0:07:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"如前所定"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"As discussed."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.98,0:07:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這么多  站長\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Here we go, chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.80,0:07:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望他們清楚自己在做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Just hope they know what they're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.73,0:07:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望我們都清楚自己在做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I hope we all know what we're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.89,0:07:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你徒步過去  混進去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You move with foot traffic and you blend in,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.97,0:07:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-特別是在酒吧周圍  -好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Especially around bars. - Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.08,0:07:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個街角原路返回一次\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Double back on every other street corner,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.82,0:07:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-至少走上兩個小時  -明白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- two hours' worth at the very least. - Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.28,0:07:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意周圍的人  比如車里的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And look for casuals -- men in parked cars,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.28,0:07:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你前后改變方向的行人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}pedestrians who change direction ahead or behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.79,0:07:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有在確保安全時才能行動\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You drop only when you are positive you are black.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.27,0:07:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對的安全\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Absolutely positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.98,0:07:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰克  我不是第一次行動了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jack, I've done this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.33,0:07:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全歸來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.65,0:09:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫斯科分站有消息嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Traffic from Moscow station?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.01,0:10:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才真是抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sorry about earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.95,0:10:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是  你知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I just -- you know, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.70,0:10:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是不同意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I didn't agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.92,0:10:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以持有自己的觀點  里克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're entitled to your opinion, Rick,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.91,0:10:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是錯誤的觀點\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Even if it's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.51,0:10:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去抽根煙嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Go for a smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.51,0:10:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在戒煙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Trying to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.79,0:10:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是好事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.07,0:10:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但愿如此\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.78,0:10:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有情況要通知我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let me know how it goes, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.96,0:12:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格萊姆斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Grimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.06,0:12:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒消息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nothing yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.79,0:12:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-有情況就通知我  -好  第一個通知你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Keep me informed. - Yeah, first to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.04,0:12:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.12,0:13:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我手快被你們扭斷了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're breaking my arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.20,0:13:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我最新情況\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Get me up to speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.37,0:13:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們正在跟巨錨做資金傳遞\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We were proceeding with the dead drop for GT Weigh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.64,0:13:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廖內德·波列修克  克格勃官員\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}KGB officer Leonid Poleshchuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.59,0:14:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只說暗號\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Encrypted names only.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.65,0:14:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少他還是個人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, for crying out loud, he's a human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.69,0:14:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟  守點規矩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Arthur. Follow protocol.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.00,0:14:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨錨的行動地點是在彼得羅夫斯基公園\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}For GT Weigh in our operational location in Petrovsky park.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.52,0:14:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的情報專員開始行動的時間是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our case officer started the operation at...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.45,0:14:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格林威治時間  14點20分\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}14:20, GMT.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.23,0:14:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前我被告知他有兩個小時\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was told he had two hours
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.32,0:14:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-來避開偵查掩護自己  -結果呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- to evade detection and go black. - And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.74,0:14:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他沒能向站長復命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He never reported back to his station chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.65,0:14:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一個聯系我們的是誰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Who was first contact to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.44,0:14:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情報專員的妻子上報了他沒回家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The case officer's wife reported that he hadn't returned home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.22,0:14:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么時候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What time was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.95,0:14:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格林威治時間  18點30分\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}18:30, GMT.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.37,0:14:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他花了兩個小時偽裝掩護\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So he took two hours to go black,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.40,0:14:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把錢放進情報點  然后被抓\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}filled the drop, was arrested,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.22,0:14:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后他妻子等了足足兩個小時才聯系我們\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and his wife took an extra two hours grace time and called us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.26,0:14:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對事實吧  大伙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We need to face facts here, people --
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.62,0:14:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們包抄了我們的情報專員\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They rolled up our case officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.06,0:14:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可能他們知道他為什么會在那\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They probably know why he was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.55,0:14:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這意味著\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.35,0:14:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨錨招供了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}GT weigh's been compromised.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.26,0:14:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早和你說了  這主意糟糕透頂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Told you. This was a really bad idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.70,0:14:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里克  現在不是怪罪別人的時候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Rick, not the moment for blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,線報員是否已招供  只是我們單方面的猜測\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Whether our asset has been compromised is a guess on our part.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.67,0:14:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可這猜測相當有說服力  華萊士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Seems like an educated guess, Wallace.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.37,0:14:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先集中注意力在已有的確定情報上吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let's just focus on what we know for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.55,0:14:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情報專員現在在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Where's our case officer now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.02,0:15:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們認為他被關押在盧比揚卡監獄\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We believe he's being held in Lubyanka prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.89,0:15:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通知國務院\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Notify the State Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.37,0:15:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知會美國駐俄大使\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Wake up the U.S. ambassador.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.51,0:15:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}盧比揚卡監獄\N蘇聯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.42,0:15:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我  我是一名美國外交官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Get your hands off me! I am an American diplomat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.37,0:15:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任職于美國大使館\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I work -- I work at the U.S. embassy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.82,0:15:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是美國的外交官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am an American diplomat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.15,0:15:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任職于美國大使館\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I work at the U.S. embassy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.17,0:15:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,20,000盧布\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}20,000 rubles.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.71,0:15:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好大一筆錢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's a lot of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.07,0:15:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是一名美國外交官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm an American diplomat
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.79,0:15:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任職于美國大使館\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}working at the U.S. embassy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.13,0:15:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在此要求通知美國大使\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I hereby request that you call the U.S. ambassador
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.76,0:15:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并告知他我受到非法拘禁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and alert him to this illegal detention.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.49,0:15:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.77,0:15:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們來說說什么是合法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let's talk of legality.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.34,0:15:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一個美國公民\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You are American citizen
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.27,0:15:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻在莫斯科市中心的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}leaving 20,000 rubles
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.20,0:15:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一處水泥缺口里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}in piece of broken concrete...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:16:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞了兩萬盧布\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}in downtown Moscow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.02,0:16:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使翻遍所有蘇聯法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}By any reading of Soviet Law,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.44,0:16:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都會被指認為犯罪活動預謀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that speaks to impending criminal activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.17,0:16:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,介意解釋一下嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You care to explain?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.90,0:16:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是一名美國外交官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm an American diplomat,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.16,0:16:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任職于美國大使館\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}working at the U.S. embassy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.94,0:16:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許是為了一個女人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Perhaps it was for a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.16,0:16:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有沒有愛上過\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Have you fallen in love
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.94,0:16:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某位俄羅斯美人呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}with one of our Russian beauties?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.80,0:16:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情婦呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hmm? A mistress? Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.15,0:16:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她希望你能來照顧她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She wants you to take care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.82,0:16:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是個...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.19,0:16:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽上去挺可信的故事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}plausible cover story.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.89,0:16:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.51,0:16:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者我們彼此敞開天窗說亮話吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Or shall we just be honest with each other? Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.58,0:16:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是什么美國外交官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You are no more American diplomat
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.70,0:16:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我也不是拉達工廠的工人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}than I am comrade worker in Lada factory!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.26,0:16:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都是間諜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We are both spies!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.55,0:16:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你被我逮了個現行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And I caught you spying!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.40,0:17:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.92,0:17:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要擺脫目前的處境  回到你家人身邊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}all you really have to do to make this all better,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.60,0:17:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真正要做的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to be released to your family,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.52,0:17:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指認我們逮捕的那個男人是你的間諜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}is confirm that the man we arrested was your asset.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.73,0:18:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有話直說  格萊姆斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey. Spit it out, Grimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.08,0:18:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的情報專員正在蹲大牢呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our case officer's sitting in a prison cell right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.78,0:18:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天知道克格勃會怎么拷問他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}God only knows how the KGB is interrogating him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.51,0:18:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會打電話給國務院  讓他們提出抗議\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll call the State Department, they'll scream and yell,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.49,0:18:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他從牢里弄出來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and we'll get him out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.67,0:18:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你真正擔心的不是這個  是不是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But that's not what you're really worried about, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.45,0:18:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個間諜  波列修克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The asset -- Poleshchuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.23,0:18:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和他一起在巴拿馬待過一個月\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I spent a month with him in Panama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.07,0:18:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他粗魯不堪  整日酗酒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Wild man, drank like a fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.97,0:18:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我漸漸開始喜歡他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But I grew to like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.63,0:18:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他給我講過一個故事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He told me this story,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.43,0:18:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說他想要用一瓶威士忌\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}said he wanted to bribe a potential recruit
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.63,0:18:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收買一名潛在間諜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}with a bottle of whiskey,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.63,0:18:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他的克格勃上司拒絕付賬\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but his KGB boss wouldn't pay for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.67,0:18:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他對此耿耿于懷\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That stuck in his craw so bad,
