Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.27,0:18:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可能是我們唯一一個\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's probably the only spy we ever got
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.88,0:18:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只用一瓶酒就買通了的間諜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}for a single bottle of booze.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.17,0:18:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可能說錯了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well... I could be wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.09,0:18:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們無法確定他是否已經招供\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We can't be sure he's been compromised.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.58,0:18:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波列修克有老婆和孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Poleshchuk has a wife and children.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.43,0:18:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他知道他在做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He knew what he was getting into.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.48,0:18:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  你確定嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Did he? Are you so sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.32,0:18:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們會把他拖到冒牌法官面前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They'll haul him in front of a phony judge,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.87,0:18:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行模擬審訊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}they'll stage a mock trial,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.69,0:19:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行宣判  判他有罪  然后...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}pronounce him guilty, sentence him, and then --
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.10,0:19:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們會把他拖到院子里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They'll drag him out into a courtyard
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.67,0:19:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,執行槍決\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and put a bullet in the back of his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.00,0:19:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊蒂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sandy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.62,0:19:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是你的錯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.36,0:19:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我堅持要他把錢藏在蘇聯境內\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I pushed to have him dead-drop the money inside the USSR.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.29,0:19:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是我  也許他現在已經自由\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If I hadn't, maybe he'd be free now,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.26,0:19:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正和他的家人團聚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}home with his family.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.13,0:19:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做的是對的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It was the right thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.02,0:19:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但事情搞砸了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But it blew up on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.20,0:19:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前為止我們還不知道為什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And we have no idea why yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.02,0:19:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格萊姆斯  繼續你的工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Grimes, you stay on task.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.25,0:19:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得努力工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You keep your nose to the grindstone,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.67,0:19:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但最重要的是  你要把生活中的一切分開\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but mostly you keep everything in your life separate --
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.77,0:19:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作  家庭  間諜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Work, family, assets.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.03,0:19:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你必須把它們分開\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You have got to compartmentalize.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.64,0:19:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道我能不能做到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't know if I can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.51,0:19:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道我是不是那樣的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't know if I'm that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.21,0:19:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你做不到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well... If you can't,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.83,0:19:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這份工作會毀了你的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}this job will tear you apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.31,0:20:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整個克格勃大樓里  只有一個地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There is only one place to have a private conversation
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.45,0:20:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能進行秘密談話\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}in entire KGB building.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.54,0:20:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}巴拿馬\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}1972
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.81,0:20:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道在哪嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And do you know where that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.83,0:20:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}男廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.99,0:20:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}沒錯  廁所是我們完成本職工作的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.12,0:20:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在酒吧里大聲談及你雇主的名字\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Broadcasting the name of your employer in a bar
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.93,0:20:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不是個明智的舉動\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}might not be the smartest move.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.43,0:20:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許我們應該換個地方接著談\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Maybe we should take this conversation someplace else.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.11,0:20:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我  我們會是最佳間諜組合\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You and I, we could be the best spy team.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.61,0:20:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就我們倆  去巴黎或是塔西提島\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Just the two of us -- Paris or maybe Tahiti.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.36,0:20:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不這么想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.18,0:20:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我不嘗試一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I would be haunted forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會一輩子心里不安的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}if I didn't at least try.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.90,0:21:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}美國大使館\N莫斯科
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.40,0:21:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是我們使館的工作人員\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's part of my diplomatic staff
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.35,0:21:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依照國際法  擁有豁免權\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and, by international law, has immunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.92,0:21:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴方觸犯了蘇維埃社會主義共和聯盟的法律\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You have violated the laws and integrity
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.00,0:21:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威脅到我國領土完整\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}of the Union of Soviet Socialist --
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.80,0:21:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我方絕對尊重\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have absolute respect
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.77,0:21:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘇聯的領土完整\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}for the territorial integrity of the Soviet Union.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.55,0:21:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并竭盡全力遵守貴國的法律\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We make every attempt to abide by your sovereign laws.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.75,0:21:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說謊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You are lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.66,0:21:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們知道貴國在我國進行間諜活動\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We know you run spies in my country.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.74,0:21:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一行為是對蘇聯的嚴重侮辱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is a terrible insult to the Soviet Union.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.13,0:21:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們絕不會把間諜安插在貴國主權范圍...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We would not employ a spy within the sovereign borders of --
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.13,0:21:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩萬盧布顯然是用來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}20,000 rubles was obviously...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.03,0:21:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-這不是問題的關鍵  -通過行賄\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- That is not the issue here. - A bribe...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.45,0:21:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以策反我國公民賣國通敵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to get our citizens to betray their country.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.00,0:21:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果別無選擇的話  我會尋求白宮介入的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If I have to get the white house involved, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.72,0:21:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他掛電話了  長官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I believe he hung up, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.51,0:21:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}盧比揚卡監獄  蘇聯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.89,0:22:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你的拘留到此為止了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You are being released from detention.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.80,0:22:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過對你的指控依舊成立\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The charges against you still stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.53,0:22:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從此刻起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}From this moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.93,0:22:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經被我蘇聯列為不受歡迎者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you are persona non grata in Soviet Union.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.14,0:22:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,限你兩個小時之內收拾個人物品\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You have two hours to collect your belongings
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.43,0:22:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離開我國\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and leave the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.28,0:22:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一份就此事件的通知已經發往你們的大使館\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A letter to this effect has been sent to your embassy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.87,0:22:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就在這  是不是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's here, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.15,0:22:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在這棟樓里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.61,0:22:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被關在另一間牢房\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In another cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.14,0:22:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們俄國人對盧比揚卡監獄流傳著一種說法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Russians have saying about Lubyanka prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.49,0:22:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說這是莫斯科最高的建筑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They call it the tallest building in Moscow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.13,0:22:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道為什么嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.80,0:23:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為從地下室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Because, from the basement,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.03,0:23:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就可以一眼望到西伯利亞\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you can see all the way to Siberia.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.50,0:23:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的情報專員已被從盧比揚卡監獄釋放\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our case officer has been released from Lubyanka.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.81,0:23:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有兩個小時離開俄國\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He has two hours to leave the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.28,0:23:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俄國佬正在把他押上飛機\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They're putting him on a plane right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.67,0:23:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  謝謝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All right. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.96,0:23:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是避免了一場危機\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}One crisis averted.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.18,0:23:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會給所有站長拍份電報\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll write to all station chiefs.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.40,0:23:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴他們之前是你負責巨錨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You handled GT Weigh in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.03,0:23:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并警告有一定可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let them know there's a possibility
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.34,0:23:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-他是被出賣的  -好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- He's been compromised. - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.68,0:23:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊蒂還有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And, Sandy...
