Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.33,0:23:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫他們再次核查各站的行動\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ask them to double check their operations.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.29,0:23:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何有機密權限的職員\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Employees with access,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.76,0:23:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通信  情報手段\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Communications, tradecraft --
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.21,0:23:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何方面只要是出一點差錯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Compromise could have come from anywhere --
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.09,0:24:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都可能導致機要信息泄露\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}a tiny mistake from any of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.08,0:24:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴他們  眼睛放尖點\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You tell them to look hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.06,0:24:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧斯丁說你們有撥往莫斯科分站的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Austin said you had an immediate-action cable
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.91,0:24:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應急聯絡專線\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to go to Como?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.71,0:24:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Uh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.41,0:24:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認識他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You knew him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.79,0:24:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.36,0:24:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還不確定他已經犧牲了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We don't know that he's been lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.77,0:24:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也對  是我的錯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're right. My mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.84,0:24:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}這趟玩的還盡興嗎  伙計
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.24,0:24:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}希望你能滿意
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.58,0:24:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}因為你的死期已經到了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.90,0:24:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}你一個蘇聯人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.65,0:24:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}還是個克格勃特工
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.49,0:24:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}曾經宣誓效忠國家
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.30,0:24:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}卻選擇背叛祖國當美國佬的走狗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.00,0:25:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}到底為什么  廖內德
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.38,0:25:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}就為了幾盧布  一雙好鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.57,0:25:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}我的兒子生病了   我必須回家
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.74,0:25:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}不過  至少他還活著 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.17,0:25:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}我的克格勃上司謝里瓦斯托夫專橫殘暴
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.37,0:25:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}所以你就置國家的安危于不顧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.45,0:25:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}我父親去世的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.93,0:25:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}連自己的葬禮都不允許我參加
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.32,0:25:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}我被激怒了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.03,0:25:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}這是一個兒子對父親的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.87,0:25:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}你能明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.49,0:25:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}這總能算得上原因了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.75,0:25:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}算個屁
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.24,0:26:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我全是照著你們要求的去做的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I did everything you told me to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.26,0:26:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我花了兩個小時反跟蹤\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I took two hours going black.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.85,0:26:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在到公園之前總算是甩干凈了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was alone well before I got to the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.83,0:26:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有可能你把尾隨者漏掉了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is there any chance you missed your tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.71,0:26:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.67,0:26:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有反跟蹤的過程都無懈可擊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, the tradecraft was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.62,0:26:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你離開大使館的時候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Did anything strike you as different,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.63,0:26:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有遇到什么不尋常的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}out of the ordinary when you left the embassy?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.03,0:26:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們每天都跟著我出大使館\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They follow me out of that embassy every single day.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.72,0:26:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都是相同的情形\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Every day, it's always the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.48,0:26:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚也是如此\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It was the same last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.69,0:26:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克格勃  他們毫不松懈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The KGB -- they're relentless.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.17,0:26:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在公園有什么發現  在你被捕之前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What about at the park, before the arrest?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.99,0:26:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么  奇怪的事物或者...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Was there anything, you know, strange or...?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.59,0:26:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看見一個人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I saw someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.99,0:26:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得可能是諜報員\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I thought it might have been the asset.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.22,0:26:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他朝我揮了揮手  不過后來...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He waved, but then...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.27,0:26:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切發生得太快了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It all happened so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.02,0:26:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們休息十分鐘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let's take a 10-minute break.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.50,0:26:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一件事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}One more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.65,0:26:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在盧比揚卡審訊我的審訊員\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My interrogator at Lubyanka
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.54,0:27:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直要我供出諜報員的名字\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}kept asking me to confirm the name of the asset
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.49,0:27:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒說  但是...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was dropping for, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.07,0:27:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得他已經知道了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I think he already knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.58,0:27:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果公園里的那個人是諜報員\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If the man in the park was the asset,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.30,0:27:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他為什么到情報傳遞點來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}why would he come to the dead drop?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.96,0:27:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情報傳遞點的關鍵目的就是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The whole point of a dead drop
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.09,0:27:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保證你與你的情報專員\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}is you aren't in the same place
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.33,0:27:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠不會出現在同一地點\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}as your case officer, ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.96,0:27:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許他怕他已經被懷疑上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Maybe he was afraid he was under suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.63,0:27:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他揮手是在警告我們的情報專員離開傳遞點\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He waved to warn our case officer off the drop.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.20,0:27:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-珊蒂  -如果是那樣的話\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Sandy. - If that's the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.63,0:27:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克格勃無法確定巨錨是間諜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the KGB wouldn't be sure GT Weigh was a spy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.90,0:27:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們需要更多的證據\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They'll need more proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.96,0:27:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊蒂  珊蒂...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sandy, Sandy...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.08,0:27:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半小時前收到的...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This came in half an hour ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.47,0:27:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從盧比揚卡內部一個低級線人處得到的消息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}From a low-level in-place source at Lubyanka.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.05,0:27:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波列修克昨天被處決了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Poleshchuk was executed yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.85,0:27:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們明早要做的第一件事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're gonna need a report to take to the Seventh Floor
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.59,0:27:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是把報告送去局長辦公室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}first thing tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.63,0:27:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里根總統今天說\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}President Reagan said today
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.71,0:28:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在日內瓦峰會上所取得的一項重大成果\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that the great measure of success at the Geneva Summit
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.31,0:28:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是與米哈伊爾·戈爾巴喬夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}was his one-on-one conversations alone
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.40,0:28:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所進行的一對一談話\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}with Mikhail Gorbachev.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.95,0:28:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘇聯通過多種方式試圖\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Soviets tried in a couple of ways
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.34,0:28:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻止美國的太空導彈防御計劃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to stop the American program for a missile defense in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.59,0:28:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽  你去哪兒了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mom, where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.28,0:28:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得跟你說一下星期六晚上的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I need to talk to you about Saturday night,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.42,0:28:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本吉·帕拉爾想帶我去參加聚會  還有...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}because Benji Parrell wants to take me to this party, and --
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.91,0:28:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一邊玩去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not now!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.82,0:28:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這很傷人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That was bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.00,0:28:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去道歉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll go apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.83,0:28:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,談談嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.67,0:28:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我不能說\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You know I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.29,0:28:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她從不在我身邊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She's never around.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.87,0:28:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在的時候總又那么討人厭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And when she is, she's so obnoxious.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.97,0:29:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真受不了待在她身邊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can't stand to be around her.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.03,0:29:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.23,0:29:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-準備好了嗎  -我想是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- You ready? - I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.33,0:29:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡短明了  切入主題\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Keep it short and to the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.83,0:29:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞特  珊蒂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Art. Sandy...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.70,0:29:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝你們前來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thanks for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.45,0:29:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,局長你認識的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You know the director.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.75,0:29:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很高興再次見到你  長官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's good to see you again, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.42,0:29:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長官  正如你所知\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sir, as you probably know,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.63,0:29:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們與巨錨的情報投送\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our dead drop to GT Weigh
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.92,0:29:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩天前在莫斯科被截擊了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}was intercepted two days ago in Moscow.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.58,0:29:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的情報專員被捕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our case officer was arrested,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.18,0:29:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們有理由相信我們的諜報員被出賣了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and we had reason to believe our asset had been compromised.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.70,0:29:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚  我們得到可靠消息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Last night, we learned with certainty
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.30,0:29:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨錨在盧比揚卡監獄被處決了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that GT Weigh had been executed in Lubyanka prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.45,0:29:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們正在對此事件展開調查\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're now beginning the process of investigating the nature --
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.68,0:29:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打斷一下  珊蒂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let me stop you there, Sandy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.11,0:29:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找借口把你叫來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I brought you here under slightly false pretenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.84,0:29:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得中情局局長\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}While I do want the D.C.I.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.22,0:29:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要聽到的是這次行動的細節\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to hear the details of the operation,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.37,0:29:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更重要的是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}more importantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.34,0:29:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有想要告訴你的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I wanted to fill you all in on something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.84,0:30:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨錨的犧牲只是冰山一角\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The compromise of GT Weigh is just the tip of the iceberg.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.73,0:30:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況比你想象的嚴重得多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The situation is far worse than you can possibly imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.99,0:30:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在過去的三個月里  我們損失了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We've lost more assets in the last three months
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.97,0:30:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比史上任何時候都要多的諜報員\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}than at practically any other time in our history.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.23,0:30:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨濤是一個極其成功的竊聽器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Gt Taw was an extremely successful tap
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.58,0:30:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它被安裝在一條位于莫斯科市中心地下的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}we'd been running on a KGB phone line underground
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.84,0:30:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克格勃電話線路上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}in central Moscow.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.59,0:30:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一機密保密級別很高\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It was a highly restricted case.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.19,0:30:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有極少數人知道它的存在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Very few people knew about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.46,0:30:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,線路很難接入\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The line was difficult to access,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.46,0:30:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們從那條線路得到的信息是無價的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but the intel we gained on it was invaluable --
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.22,0:30:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行動的詳細計劃  涉及官員姓名\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}operational detail, officer names,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.67,0:30:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地址  還有克格勃的戰略情報\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}locations, KGB strategic intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.54,0:30:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三個月之前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Three months ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.77,0:30:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當一名特工人員從監聽線路上取回錄音帶時\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}while an officer was retrieving tapes from a tapped line,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.08,0:30:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警報被觸發了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}an alarm sounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.31,0:30:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們安裝報警裝置是為了提醒情報專員\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We had set up the alarm to warn case officers
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.73,0:30:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦監聽線路被人發現\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}in case the tap had become compromised,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.30,0:30:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果果不其然\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}which it had.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.06,0:30:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那只是開始\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That was just the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.95,0:31:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上個月\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Last month,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.64,0:31:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在慕尼黑工作了很長時間的間諜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}a longtime asset for us in Munich
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.71,0:31:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到克格勃讓其返回莫斯科的指令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}was recalled by the KGB to Moscow.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.23,0:31:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們說他成年的兒子有健康問題\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They told him his grown son had a health issue
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.35,0:31:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要他立刻回家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}which needed his immediate attention back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.39,0:31:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當這名特工給在蘇聯的朋友打電話時\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When the asset called family friends in the Soviet Union
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.49,0:31:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才確定他兒子生病的事是假的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and established that the story about his son was false,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.38,0:31:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們建議他立即撤離\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}we recommended he be exfiltrated immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.69,0:31:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克格勃追他追的很緊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The KGB came after him, hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.57,0:31:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們很幸運\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We got lucky,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.35,0:31:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那名間諜毫發無傷的逃走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and the asset escaped unharmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.84,0:31:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他現在身處美國本土的一間安全屋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's currently in a safe house inside the U.S.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.85,0:31:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但巨錨就沒那么幸運了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But GT Weigh, obviously, is not.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.02,0:31:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是克格勃走了狗屎運\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Either the KGB has gotten extremely lucky of late
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.63,0:31:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就一定是我們有了大麻煩了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}or we have a serious problem on our hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.01,0:31:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何  我們遭受了重創\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Whatever it is, we are getting hammered,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.84,0:31:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在蘇聯布置的情報網絡正在遭受破壞\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}destroying our eyes and ears inside the Soviet Union.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.72,0:31:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更不用說殺人的那些事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not to mention killing people.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.14,0:31:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事要盡可能先壓在局里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This needs to stay in the building as long as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.95,0:31:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總統并不知情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The president doesn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.33,0:31:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媒體當然更不可能知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The press certainly cannot know.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.57,0:31:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們必須盡快把這事查清\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We need to figure this out fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.17,0:32:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在東蘇分部的人馬\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your team in S.E. Division
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.41,0:32:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須在我們徹底失去情報來源\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}needs to get their heads back in the game
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.53,0:32:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并輸掉這該死的冷戰之前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}before we go completely blind
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.82,0:32:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重整旗鼓\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and lose the damn cold war.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.42,0:32:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論什么困難  你都能擊敗它\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Whatever it is, you will beat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.13,0:32:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我遇到過的最聰明  最堅強\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're the smartest, the toughest,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.83,0:32:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最英勇的女人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The most heroic woman I've ever met.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.98,0:32:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那沒問題嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.44,0:32:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的意思是  你真的想要那么堅強\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I mean, do you want a wife who can be that tough,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.76,0:32:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把生活分割出去的妻子嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Who compartmentalizes her life?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.06,0:32:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家庭在一邊  工作在另一邊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Family here, work there?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.22,0:32:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且對她最愛的那個人隱瞞很多秘密\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Who keeps secrets from the one person she loves most?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.18,0:32:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們每個人都有秘密  桑迪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We all keep secrets, Sandy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.98,0:32:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想象一下如果我們了解凱莉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Imagine how much we'd worry
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.16,0:32:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生活中發生的每一件事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}if we knew every single thing about Kelly's life...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.82,0:32:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道她說的每一句話  該有多擔心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...if we knew every word she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.19,0:33:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些時候秘密能讓人遠離傷害\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sometimes a secret keeps the hurt away.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.95,0:33:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道  我娶你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You know, I married you...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.25,0:33:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為我清楚地知道你要去拯救世界\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}because it was clear to me you were out to save the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.87,0:33:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論付出什么代價  你都會做到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Whatever it took, you would make that happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.58,0:33:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當你真的做到時  我會為你而驕傲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and that I would be proud of you when you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.23,0:33:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個家的每一個人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Everyone in this family
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.64,0:33:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都知道你為什么要擔起這份責任\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}knows why you do what you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.29,0:33:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你自己知道嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But do you know why you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.60,0:33:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你是個勇士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Because you are a warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.05,0:33:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了保護你的祖國\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Protecting your country.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.87,0:33:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了我們\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You do it for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.18,0:33:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守護我們的安全\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To keep us safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.81,0:33:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回去工作了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have to go back to the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.34,0:33:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不等你睡了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I won't be waiting up.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.08,0:35:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公園里揮手的那個人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The man in the park who waved.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.07,0:35:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你整晚都在這里嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You been here all night?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.89,0:35:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是為了警告我們的情報專員離開\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He wasn't trying to warn our case officer off the drop.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.15,0:35:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是要確保情報專員看到他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He was making sure our case officer saw him,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.28,0:35:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意到他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}noticed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.09,0:35:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直沒睡過覺  對嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You didn't get any sleep, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.70,0:35:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諜報員揮手的時候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The asset was here
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.02,0:35:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就站在這里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When he waved.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.61,0:35:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情報專員說\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The case officer said
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.23,0:35:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克格勃從這棟樓出現\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that the KGB came from around this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.58,0:35:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看看這公園的地形\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, look at the geography of the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.41,0:35:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諜報員是可以看到他們的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The asset would have seen them.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.74,0:35:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他應該知道克格勃官員就在那里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He would've known the KGB officers were there,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.52,0:35:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埋伏  蹲守  也就是說\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}hiding, waiting, which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.77,0:35:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是那個諜報員\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He wasn't the asset.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.73,0:35:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在裝樣子  是個替身\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He was a plant, a double.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.68,0:35:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.39,0:35:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整件事都是陷阱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The whole thing was a setup.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.66,0:35:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克格勃就是要確保\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The KGB wanted to make sure
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.25,0:35:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得到的情報是說\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that it got reported back to us
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.53,0:35:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個諜報員被跟蹤并且在公園被逮捕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that the asset was followed and arrested in the park --
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.56,0:35:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣看起來好像他們剛剛知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to make it look like they just figured out
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.05,0:35:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波列修克是個間諜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that Poleshchuk was a spy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.84,0:35:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許他們已經懷疑  對他進行了監控\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Maybe that they had suspicions, had him under surveillance,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.37,0:35:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他們已經知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but they knew,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.69,0:36:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且已經知道有一陣子了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and they must have known for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.97,0:36:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我甚至敢打賭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'd put even money
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.19,0:36:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波列修克在被他們處決之前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that Poleshchuk had been sitting in a jail
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.24,0:36:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經在監獄里待了一個月\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}for a month when they executed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.89,0:36:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公園里整個行動只是為了迷惑我們\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The whole operation in the park is meant to confuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.40,0:36:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純粹是演戲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Pure theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.68,0:36:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他們這么大費周章  那只可能是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And they'd only put on a play if --
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.37,0:36:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們在掩蓋更重要的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If they were covering up something more important --
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.86,0:36:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常非常重要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}a lot more important.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.50,0:36:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克格勃在掩蓋真正的問題\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}KGB's hiding the true problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.27,0:36:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們能得到局里的情報  亞特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They have an in to the agency, Art.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.74,0:36:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們打入我們內部了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They've cracked us.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.60,0:36:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家  睡個覺  這是命令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Go home, get some sleep. That's an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.44,0:36:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  格萊姆斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, and, Grimes --
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.29,0:36:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天見\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.70,0:37:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一大早要不要來一根提提神\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Want to grab an early smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.04,0:37:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我戒了  再不抽了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No. I quit -- for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.47,0:37:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要走了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.58,0:37:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  來半天了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah. Been here a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.04,0:37:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我  巨錨的問題解決了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tell me -- solve GT Weigh?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.20,0:37:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.62,0:37:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們會解決的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But we'll get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.21,0:37:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見  里克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}See you, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.36,0:37:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.25,0:37:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}絕密
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.26,0:38:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吃完營養早餐誰也不許出家門\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nobody leaves this house without a nutritious breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.55,0:38:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廣告里怎么說的來著\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What do they say in the commercials?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.81,0:38:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一天中最重要的一頓飯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The most important meal of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.67,0:38:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一身是去學校的行頭嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, that's a school outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.12,0:38:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是睡衣  媽媽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}These are pajamas, mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.09,0:38:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是很得體的睡衣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah, well, they're appropriate pajamas.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.17,0:38:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜歡  加里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I like them. Gary?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.71,0:38:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也喜歡  男孩子們也會喜歡的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Love them. Boys will, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.84,0:38:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒吃夠的話自己再拿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Help yourself if you want any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.75,0:38:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好豐盛啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A feast.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.51,0:38:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楓糖漿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Maple syrup.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.28,0:38:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們有人打入了我們內部\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They got an in to our setup.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.63,0:38:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得一層層撥開疑云找到他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We just got to peel back the layers and find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.24,0:38:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你的看法嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your concept?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.51,0:38:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  團隊一起得出的結論\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, a group came up with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.62,0:39:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主要是格萊姆斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Grimes, mostly.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.69,0:39:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.81,0:39:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就開始行動\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let's get to work, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.69,0:39:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亡羊補牢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Stop the bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.47,0:39:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼知道接下來他們會給我們用什么損招\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}God only knows what they'll throw at us next.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.28,0:39:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}羅馬
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.17,0:39:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  我叫維塔利·尤琴科\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, my name is Vitaly Yurchenko.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.98,0:39:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在大使館前面的電話亭里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am phoning you from the telephone box
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.37,0:39:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你打電話\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}in front of the embassy.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.98,0:39:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是克格勃負責反間諜的資深上校\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am senior counterintelligence colonel in the KGB...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.60,0:39:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要投誠\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and I wish to defect.
